  "detailed_description": "Get out! Snakes! It's a new way to play the famous 90's cell phone classic, now you're not the snake, you're the snake's target!<br><br>Save your apple friends on an adventure with 5 different worlds that tell the story of how a heroic red apple, guardian of the green apple tree, saves green apples from a terrible snake attack!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393120/extras/328a19aa0c3bff8b6bd129236e758b8e.avif?t=1622249630\" width=64 height=64 /></span>                              <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393120/extras/43df431360f9755de6ca360c15e249d3.avif?t=1622249630\" width=64 height=64 /></span>                         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393120/extras/38204ddbeab39d2b6b6792f59c542428.avif?t=1622249630\" width=64 height=64 /></span>   <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1393120/extras/47115c62abac411df2b92785d6c4bf91.avif?t=1622249630\" width=64 height=64 /></span><br><br>So ... save the apples before the snake attacks, but stay tuned, as you too can be attacked!<br><br>Features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>5 different worlds with 5 levels each<br><br></li><li>Singleplayer or multiplayer story mode<br><br></li><li>2 players battle mode<br><br></li><li>Original songs<br><br></li><li>Original characters<br><br></li><li>Great repetition value</li></ul>",
